  <brief_title>Magnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI) in Asymptomatic Patients With Juvenile Idiopathic Arthritis (JIA)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Diagnostic Value of MRI and Ultrasound in Patients With JIA</official_title>
